snippet.description:
Watch all the episode of Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum here: https://bit.ly/3zNNsGu

Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum | Episode 33 | Digitally Presented by Master Paints , foodpanda , Sunsilk & Skin White | Fahad Mustafa | Hania Aamir | 29 October 2024 | ARY Digital Drama 

The drama revolves around the concept of ‘Opposites Attract’ where Hania aka Sharjeena will portray the role of a bibliophile, topper and a sorted girl with a practical approach while Fahad’s character is a little laid-back.

Writer: Farhat Ishtiaq
Directed by: Badar Mehmood
 
Cast:
Fahad Mustafa as Mustafa
Hania Aamir as Sharjeena
Emmad Irfani as Adeel
Javed Sheikh as Iftekhar 
Bushra Ansari as Shagufta
Maya Khan as Sidra
Naeema Butt as Rubab
Tauseeq Haider,
Yousuf Bashir Qureshi.

snippet.title: MIXTURE Snack | DIWALI Special Traditional Mixture Recipe Cooking In Village | South Indian Snacks
snippet.description:
Mixture Recipe is a popular snack recipe in South India, especially in Tamil Nadu, Kerala and Karnataka. Today, we are cooking this recipe as a Diwali Special. The specialty of this snack is its mixed taste. 

To enhance the flavor of this mixture, we use Boondi, Fried Nuts, Fried Spices, and other healthy ingredients, along with Omappodi.

The taste is memorable!

Jaan Nisar 2nd Last Episode 64 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 25th October 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.description:
Today I am going to share you a popular Indian sweet motichur laddu recipe on the occasion of Diwali. Motichur Laddu is Originating in North India, Motichur Laddu is traditionally made during festivals and celebrations, like Diwali, weddings, and other joyous occasions, making it a beloved delicacy across India. Its rich flavor, bright orange color, and sweet aroma make it irresistible to sweet lovers.Here I'm sharing easy way of making boondi without boondi jhara and a simple technique to make laddu juicy ever at home.Do try this juicy motichur laddu recipe at home and leave your valuable feedback in comment section🤗.

#CitadelHoneyBunnyOnPrime, New Series, Nov 7

Prime Video India Presents
Citadel Honey Bunny Official Trailer 2

About:
When stuntman Bunny recruits struggling actress Honey for a side gig, they are hurled into a high-stakes world of action, espionage and betrayal. Years later, as their dangerous past catches up, the estranged Honey and Bunny must reunite and fight to protect their young daughter Nadia.
A Series By Raj & DK

Starring: Varun Dhawan, Samantha, Kay Kay Menon, Simran, Saqib Saleem, Sikandar Kher, Soham Majumdar, Shivankit Parihar, and Kashvi Majmundar. 

Directed by Raj & DK 
Developed by Sita R Menon 
Written by Sita R Menon, Raj & DK 
Produced by D2R Films & Amazon MGM Studios 
Executive produced by The Russo Brothers’ AGBO and Raj & DK 
Executive Producers for All the Series in The World Of Citadel: Anthony Russo, Joe Russo, Angela Russo-Otstot, Scott Nemes, David Weil, Midnight Radio. 
Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma 
Supervising Producer: Pravin Khairnar (Quercus Productions) 
Director Of Photography: Johan Heurlin Aidt 
Production Designer: Meenal Agarwal 
Editor: Sumeet Kotian 
Screenplay: Sita R Menon, Raj & DK 
Dialogues: Sumit Arora 
Action Directors: Yannick Ben Haddou, Diyan Georigiev Hristov, Aejaz Gulab 
Sound Design: Sanjay Maurya & Allwin Rego 
Background Music: Aman Pant 
Costume Designer: Ameira Punvani 
Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA Second 
Unit Director: Tusshar Seyth 
Associate Director: Chesta Goswami 
Showrunners' Associate: Manisha K Makwana 
First Assistant Director: Moen Sheikh 
Post-Production Supervisor: Jespal Nadar 
Post Production Supervisor: Gautmik 
Post-Production Coordinator: Manisha K Makwana 
Line Producers: Kalyani Warner, Rrahil Deshmukh 
Production Manager: Utkarsha Kohli 
VFX Producer: Variate Studio LLP 
Title Sequence Designed By: Rech Films LLP 
Second Unit Director Of Photography: Tarun Achpal 
Special Advisor: Bimal Parekh

Official Release Date Nov 7, 2024 on Prime Video India.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

#CitadelHoneyBunnyOnPrime #trailer #officialtrailer #primevideoindia

snippet.title: Ek Diwali Aisi Bhi | Biggest Crossover of Take A Break
snippet.description:
Ever wondered how those Diwali sketches come to life? In our latest comedy video, "Ek Diwali Aisi Bhi," we take you behind the scenes for a hilarious peek into our writers' room as they brainstorm ideas for a Diwali sketch! 🎆🤣
Join our team of writers as they toss around the most outlandish, over-the-top, and downright ridiculous ideas for the ultimate Diwali-themed video. From traditional family gatherings gone hilariously wrong to bizarre plot twists involving our IP's, each suggestion brings its own flavor of chaos and comedy.

#kaamwalibai #takeabreak #shortsbreak

snippet.title: Drop the Beat | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
Drop the Beat is an electrifying rap where participants, squad bosses, and judges come together to perform as one, creating an unforgettable experience. With everyone bringing their unique style and energy, the track turns into a high-energy celebration, blending voices, beats, and camaraderie for a blast that embodies unity and pure hip-hop joy.



Song Credits
Track Name: Drop the Beat
Written & Performed By: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,LashcurryRaga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna, 
Primary Artist: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar
Track Name: Drop the beat

Singer/Performed By/Cast: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Lyricist/Written By: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna

Lyrics


Jizzy & Talha 
Bhool Chuk Maaf First time it is.
Hume ab tak nai nikala, Good Sign it is
MTV badi ghadi samne lagado
Taki Ikka bhai can know what time it is.

Raga bhai aaya phone, Bole pocket dail hai.
EPR ki small talk bhi Rocket Science hai.
DMC ke DMS pura DHH
Friend circle ka sirf radius 8 Mile hai

Raftaar bhai is back like mihir virani
Rapper kandhe pe uthaya jaise bees litre paani
Jab dino bhai the.. naturally funny  
To hume kyun bulaya jokes marwane??

EPR
Musht-e-khaak
Khamoshi raeth si ghadiyon mein
Raqs e hasti hathkadiyon mein
Paav phisle toh daldal mein 

Barg-e-khizaan 
Fizaao mein teri himmat hai
Udne ki teri shiddat pe
Havaon ko na fursat de

charagh-e-junoon
Misl-e-Abr-e-baharon mein

Behre in badlon mein
raushni tere praharo se 

Gulshan e dahr ke kagaz ko tu awaaz de
Taqdiir-e-aasman mein siyahi teri azaad hai

Bleed ink

Raga
You know I’m all about the rage jab baat ho mere squad ki
Daabke vocal chords jazbaat nikaale opps ke
Bars so dope I get you high on my aushadhi 
Put you in a vibe in a second | sorcery 

Ye medicine vilaayti
Hum hai Home grown remedies 
Soch kratikaari like menime no feminist 
Dil ke khole raaz ye siyaahi failegi panno pe 
Ab state of mind lashcurry 
Im mad trippin pehle si hi 

Im one of the last real ones in the game 
When I’m done the it’s done, I’m big pun of this game 
I’m the one who brings fun in this game 
So, this big bad man is in this building to stay

Dino 
Ye sachin sare hum yaha ke ramakanth hai
Ye mic mai aaye toh toh chote hum sama bandh de
Hai kalakar hai bade tabhi Shama mangte
Ye kmzoro ka stage nahi, ye jagah Bombay
Ye booth mai ghuse toh , sabko bhoot bana de
Ye loop mai bajengae, mic mai thgook baha ke
Hum guth mai chalte hai, aur hum loot machate
Sare brutal hai log. yeh hai grop savasher

Aditya bhai kaha hai ye toh Mai madari hai
Ye safar acha katega insane savari hai
EPR RAA IKKA RAGA DMC
AUR Shoutout to the girl,s JO YE gama chala rahi hai




Ikka
Do yaar hustle chaar 
Parkhenge ki kaun badiya kalakaar 
Hoga kaun ithihasic abki baar 
Kaun karega baaakiyon ko sabko dar kinaar
Competition or tough hoga abki baar 
Sath denge Dino dee raga Epr 
Hustle hone wala 4 gunna crazy hai 
Kyunki wapis aayeya mera bhai the og is back raftaar


Raftaar
hustle ki mehfil me swaagat taaqat likhai ki
dikhai di to kala ki janta bani himaiti
kachii kadi ki taakein hum ghadi aati vidai ki
nibhai kalakaari jisne uska pen hai mighty
tujhme kala bhari tabhi tu invited
decide hoga hustle bas missile ban tu guided
profile hogi badhi teri badhegi ab brightness
never gonna fall baawe WE STAND UNITED
KABHI JEET KABHI LOSS
NO SIDES NO TOSS
YAHAN SE GAYE TO MILNA ON TOP
THIS IS HIP HOP AND WE DONT STOP

snippet.title: Dhanteras पर पूजा का मुहूर्त और खरीदारी का मुहूर्त क्या होगा, किन ख़ास बातों का ख्याल रखें ?
snippet.description:
सारी सफाई के कार्यक्रम धनतेरस के पूर्व निपटा लें,धनतेरस के दिन तक सफाई जारी न रखें. इस दिन केवल कुबेर की पूजा न करें , धन्वन्तरी देवता की उपासना भी जरूर करें. अगर इस दिन धातुओं का क्रय करना है तो सोना , पीतल चांदी या स्टील खरीदना चाहिए. दीपावली के लिए गणेश-लक्ष्मी की मूर्तियाँ और अन्य पूजन सामग्री भी इसी दिन क्रय करें. धन तेरस के दिन लोहा खरीदने से बचना चाहिए. इस दिन थोड़ा बहुत दान भी जरूर करें , और यह दान निर्धनों में करें तो ज्यादा अच्छा होगा. 
#Dhanteras  #ShailendraPandey

snippet.title: Introducing the all-new Mac mini | Apple
snippet.description:
The all-new Mac mini is five by five inches of pure power and purpose. With a wide array of ports, now on the front and back. Redesigned around Apple silicon to unleash the full speed and capabilities of the M4 and M4 Pro chips. And built for Apple Intelligence. Mac mini is the new definition of efficiency — and the first carbon neutral Mac.

Learn more about Mac mini: https://apple.co/3YIl7f1

Episode 4228: Guruji's Double Trouble
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak and his friends are stumped on how to arrange a meeting between Varun, his boss, and Bade Guruji, especially since Varun is already acquainted with Bapuji. Can they find a fake Bade Guruji in time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4228 | 29 Oct 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene 2 | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

Taarak worries whether Bapuji will make it in time to pose as Bade Guruji for Varun. Will everything go smoothly with their pretend meeting?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: 1 ലക്ഷം മുടക്കി മൈക്കിൾ ഒരു കാർ
snippet.description:
***Connect With Us**

Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/ebulljet
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/e_bull_jet
Twitter: https://twitter.com/EBINVAR11589819
TikTok:  https://www.tiktok.com/@ebulljet

CONTACT US: 
Whatsapp no: https://wa.me/919496502055

***About Our Channel***

Van life is very common in western countries. So in this channel at E Bull Jet, we are featuring van life in India. This channel will showcase the real-life in India and nearby countries.

We are Abin and Libin, siblings belonging to Irutty, a locality in Kannur District of Kerala, India. We aim to explore India and nearby countries in a van that's converted into a home. In this journey, we will sleep, cook, and travel in our van and will ex cover places at minimal expenses.  

We would like to bring our Van life though this channel - E BULL JET

പാശ്ചാത്യ രാജ്യങ്ങളിൽ ഉള്ള പോലെ നമ്മുടെ രാജ്യത്തും ഒരു വാൻ ലൈഫ് നടത്തുകയും അതിന്റെ മാസ്മരിക കാഴ്ചകൾ പ്രിയപെട്ടവരിലേക്ക് എത്തിക്കുകയും ആണ് 'ഈ ബുൾ ജെറ്റ്' എന്ന ഈ കൊച്ചു ചാനൽ കൊണ്ട് ഞങ്ങൾ ഉദ്ദേശിക്കുന്നത്.

കണ്ണൂർ ജില്ലയിലെ ഇരുട്ടി എന്ന പ്രദേശത്തു ജീവിക്കുന്ന സഹോദരങ്ങളാണ് ഞങ്ങൾ, പേര് എബിൻ, ലിബിൻ. നമ്മുടെ രാജ്യവും, അയാൾ രാജ്യങ്ങളും കുറഞ്ഞ ചിലവിൽ കാണുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം. അതിനായി ഒരു മിനി വാൻ ഞങ്ങൾ വീടാക്കി മാറ്റി അതിൽ യാത്ര ചെയുന്നു, വഴിയിൽ പാചകം ചെയ്തു കുറഞ്ഞു ചിലവിൽ ലോകം കാണുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം. 

ഞങ്ങൾ കാണുന്നതും കേള്കുന്നതുമായ കാര്യങ്ങൾ ഈ ചാനലിൽ കൂടെ പങ്കുവെക്കുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം.

PLEASE SUBSCRIBE TO THIS CHANNEL AND ENABLE NOTIFICATIONS: 
"Van Life Is our Passion"
"Your dream our world
This is our vision and mission - E BULL JET

Dream with Us. Thank You. :)

snippet.title: Dr. Hathi की हँसी पर Jetha का Reaction | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Old Gems
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

In this episode, Taarak comes up with an idea to ask Dr. Hathi and his family to leave Gokuldham Society. Everyone is puzzled by Dr. Hathi's constant laughter. It’s revealed at the end that the ladoos he ate in the morning were made with bhang, causing the laughter! Meanwhile, Mehta has a conversation with Anjali about being patriotic. What will happen next? Watch to find out.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 305
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethatheroastking #tmkocmemes #tmkocold #taarakmehta #jethalalcomedy #dayaben #bhide #popatlal #babitaji #comedyshow #comedyvideo #comedymemes 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Taarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Old Gems' : 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTNuXI_HVBQHzw7Odv4Fj0A

snippet.title: No Filter: Nia Sharma
snippet.description:
Hello Ji, Namaste Dooston Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Fir Se Swagat Hai!

इस Episode में हम Nia Sharma के Diverse Life को Explore करते हैं, जिसमें उनकी Journey Daily Soaps से लेकर एक Fashion Icon तक का सफर शामिल है। Nia अपने Acting Career की शुरुआत, Evolving TV industry के बारे में अपने Views, और Fashion पर अपने Thoughts को Candid तरीके से Share करेंगी। वह अपने दो सबसे अच्छे Friends के साथ अपने Equation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, जिन्हें वह प्यार से "Kids" कहती हैं। Marriage, Laughter Shows, और Sudesh Lehri के साथ काम करने के अपने Experience को भी Express करेंगी। हम उनकी Confidence, Male Attention को कैसे Handle करती हैं, और Brands के साथ उनके Negotiation के Experience पर भी चर्चा करेंगे। Nia अपने भाई, Vinay Sharma के साथ अपने Relation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, और किस तरह के Projects पर वह आगे काम करना चाहती हैं इस पर भी चर्चा होगी। Nia यह भी बताएंगी कि क्या उन्हें Cooking आती है, और YouTube और 'Laughter Chef' Show पर अपनी राय भी देंगी। अंत में, हम उनके Anchoring और Hosting को लेकर उनके Perspective को भी Explore करेंगे!

Yeh Episode Nia Sharma Ke Life Aur Personality Ki Ek Khubsurat Jhalak Hai, Dekhte Rahiye Bharti TV!

#niasharma #bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya  #lolpodcast #podcast

इस Episode में हम Nia Sharma के Diverse Life को Explore करते हैं, जिसमें उनकी Journey Daily Soaps से लेकर एक Fashion Icon तक का सफर शामिल है। Nia अपने Acting Career की शुरुआत, Evolving TV industry के बारे में अपने Views, और Fashion पर अपने Thoughts को Candid तरीके से Share करेंगी। वह अपने दो सबसे अच्छे Friends के साथ अपने Equation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, जिन्हें वह प्यार से "Kids" कहती हैं। Marriage, Laughter Shows, और Sudesh Lehri के साथ काम करने के अपने Experience को भी Express करेंगी। हम उनकी Confidence, Male Attention को कैसे Handle करती हैं, और Brands के साथ उनके Negotiation के Experience पर भी चर्चा करेंगे। Nia अपने भाई, Vinay Sharma के साथ अपने Relation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, और किस तरह के Projects पर वह आगे काम करना चाहती हैं इस पर भी चर्चा होगी। Nia यह भी बताएंगी कि क्या उन्हें Cooking आती है, और YouTube और 'Laughter Chef' Show पर अपनी राय भी देंगी। अंत में, हम उनके Anchoring और Hosting को लेकर उनके Perspective को भी Explore करेंगे!

Yeh Episode Nia Sharma Ke Life Aur Personality Ki Ek Khubsurat Jhalak Hai, Dekhte Rahiye Bharti TV!

#niasharma #bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya  #lolpodcast #podcast 

TIMESTAMPS:

(00:00) - Precap
(00:55) - Introduction & Understanding Nia Sharma
(05:11) - Daily Soaps & Views on Fashion
(08:10) - Story Behind Two Kids: "Nia's Best Friends"
(09:20) - Views on Marriage, Laughter Shows & Sudesh Lehri
(11:13) - Negotiation with Brands & People
(18:24) - How Nia Sharma Started Her Acting Career
(22:25) - Confidence, Male Attention & Marriage
(32:54) - Does Nia Know How to Cook?
(34:40) - What Type of Work Does Nia Want to Do?
(39:29) - Nia Sharma's Bond with Brother Vinay Sharma
(44:04) - Nia's Thoughts on YouTube & Laughter Chef
(48:25) - Nia's Perception on Anchoring & Hosting
(51:39) - End Note

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

The inhabitants of a society call CID to complain about one of their inhabitants named Vikram who has a gun with him. CID goes into interrogating and in a fight between Daya and Vikram, Vikram gets shot. Upon further investigation in his flat, CID finds photographs of victims who have been tied up. What does Vikram do? Watch this episode to find out.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 840
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2024 #LatestTV #LatestFromTV #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #latestcid #cid #cidlatestepisode#cidnewepisode #hinditvserial #latestepisode #newepisode #tvserial #hindiserial #hindishow #tvshow #livcrime #dayaaurabhijeetkidosti

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Daya Aur Abhijeet Ki Dosti' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIVH-HhI_BSk3AH2q5PUHy_R
